<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[ح]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c4">[تَبَدَّحَ]</span>،<span class="c5"> التَّبَدُّحُ:</span> حُسن مشية المرأة.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c4">[ل]</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c4">[تَبَدَّلَ]</span> الشيء بالشيء: إِذا أخذه عوضاً منه،<span class="c5"> قال اللّاه تعالى:</span> وَمَنْ يَتَبَدَّلِ الْكُفْرَ بِالْإِيماانِ <span class="c2">«١»</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>و <span class="c4">[تَبَدَّى]</span>: يقال: تَبَدَّى فلان: إِذا أقام بالبادية.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c4">[همزة]</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c4">[تَبَدَّأَ]</span> بالشيء، مهموز، من الابتداء<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>... التَّفَاعُل<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c4">[ح]</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c4">[تَبَادَحَ]</span>: يقال: هم يتَبادَحُون بالكرة:<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>أي يضربونها بينهم.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
